Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:38.29,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur5}那微显成熟{\c&HBFC3F4&}色{\c&HD8F5E1&}彩的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:43.17,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur5}我害羞地悄悄{\c&HBFC3F4&}藏{\c&HD8F5E1&}起来
