Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:59.73,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur5}呐 如今我这人也是一味 {\c&HBFC3F4&}「迷茫」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:04.83,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur5}那天对{\c&HBFC3F4&}你{\c&HD8F5E1&}说的话语到现在才想起
